          <title>

            <string language="x-mt-de">Enzyminhibitoren</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Inhibiteurs d'enzyme</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Inibidores de enzyme</string>

          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows how inhibitor molecules that bind into active sites of enzymes result to (a) competitive  inhibition and (b)non-competitive inhibition.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt, wie Hemmnismoleküle, die 
in aktive Sites der Enzyme binden, (a) zur konkurrierenden Hemmung 
resultieren und (b)non-konkurrierende Hemmung.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre comment les molécules 
d'inhibiteur qui lient dans les sites actifs des enzymes résultent 
(a) à l'inhibition concurrentielle et (inhibition 
b)non-concurrentielle.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra como as moléculas do 
inibidor que ligam em locais ativos dos enzymes resultam (a) à 
inibição do competidor e (inibição b)non-do competidor.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra come le molecole 
dell'inibitore che si legano nei luoghi attivi degli enzimi risultano 
(a) ad inibizione competitiva e (inibizione b)non-competitiva.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση επιδεικνύει πώς τα μόρια 
ανασταλτικών παραγόντων που δεσμεύουν στις ενεργές περιοχές των 
ενζύμων οδηγούν (α) στην ανταγωνιστική παρεμπόδιση και 
(b)non-competitive την παρεμπόδιση.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra cómo las moléculas 
del inhibidor que atan en sitios activos de enzimas resultan (a) a la 
inhibición competitiva y (inhibición b)non-competitiva.</string>
          </description>
